				<h3 class="block-content-title"><a href="/issues/37/an-evening-with-robert-bly">An Evening With Robert Bly</a></h3>
					<p class="block-content-subtitle subtitle"></p>
		

							<ul class="block-content-meta list-inline-border tiny"><li>
							By <a class="meta-article-contributors" href="/contributors/robert-bly">Robert Bly</a></li><li><a href="/issues/37">July 1978</a></li></ul>

		

					</div>


														<a href="/issues/37" class="block-content-photo cover-thumb">
					
					<img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg xmlns%3D'http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg' viewBox%3D'0 0 560 728'%2F%3E"
		data-src=https://226391-691236-raikfcquaxqncofqfm.stackpathdns.com/thumbs/140x182r/2016-10/037.jpg data-src-retina=https://226391-691236-raikfcquaxqncofqfm.stackpathdns.com/thumbs/280x364r/2016-10/037.jpg
